Day 22 of #100daysofcode challenge
‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî
Today I decided to take a little break from the code after a blistering Sunday hackathon! Instead spent the evening fannying around with screen recording and video cropping software.
‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî
I used a bit of software called OBS Studio to record my screen. Then I used an app on my iPhone called Video Crop to yeah, crop it lol. The only file format that seemed to work was .MOV and transferring the files from windows to iOS was fun to say the least.
‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî
I came across a little website called snapdrop.net which is basically meant to be like air drop but for windows. Lovely looking clean site, great ux... and just doesn‚Äôt work for me lol. So I ended up emailing them üòî
‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî
Anyways I hope you enjoy my first video. If you‚Äôre not feeling it please tell me what you would like to see. I‚Äôm very open to new ideas on content ‚ò∫Ô∏è
